<br><br><br>
Example settings ...<br>
From = your cell # --> <b>4165550000</b><br>
Who0 = contact name --> <b>Bob</b><br>
Num0 = email-to-txt addr --> <b>4165551111@sms.rogers.com</b><br><br>
Check your email-to-txt addr with your hotmail/gmail ... account!!<br>
If you receive txts from hotmail/gmail, the same addr work with this app.
